node.title: 17yo charged with murder of Central Queensland woman Rene Latimore
node.alt: a woman in a black and white shirt smiles at the camera
node.description: Police have charged a teenager with one count of murder, but have not yetÂ revealed whether he was known to Ms Latimore.
node.content: ["A 17-year-old man has been arrested over the murder of Central Queensland woman Rene Latimore.\u00a0", "The 31-year-old went missing from a rural property in Koumala, south of Mackay, in early August.\u00a0", "Several weeks later\u00a0her body was found at the property\u00a0where she had been living with family.", "On Friday morning, police charged a teenager with one count of murder.\u00a0", "Detective Inspector Jack Savage said police could not reveal whether he was known to Ms Latimore.", "More to come.\u00a0"]
